flowchart TD
    subgraph MH09["MH-09: Diary User Flow"]
        J1[User opens My Diary] --> J2[Timeline view]
        J2 --> J3["Auto-populated entries:<br/>Practice attended<br/>Check-in submitted<br/>Feedback given"]
        J3 --> J4{User action?}
        J4 -->|Add note| J5[Text editor opens]
        J4 -->|View entry| J6[Entry detail]
        J4 -->|Filter| J7[By date or practice or state]
        J5 --> J8[Save private note]
        J8 --> J9[Entry linked to practice]
        
        J10[After practice] --> J11[Prompt: Add reflection?]
        J11 --> J12{User responds?}
        J12 -->|Yes| J5
        J12 -->|Later| J13[Reminder in 24h]
        J12 -->|No| J14[No reminder]
    end
